<topic id='element_radiotherapy_diagnosis__icd_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: RADIOTHERAPY DIAGNOSIS (ICD) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_radiotherapy_diagnosis__icd_">RADIOTHERAPY DIAGNOSIS (ICD)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_clinical_classification_code">CLINICAL CLASSIFICATION CODE</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_radiotherapy_diagnosis__icd_">RADIOTHERAPY DIAGNOSIS (ICD)</xref>
 is the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_international_classification_of_diseases__icd_">International Classification of Diseases (ICD)</xref>
 code for 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient_diagnosis">PATIENT DIAGNOSIS</xref>
 for a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 receiving 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_radiotherapy">Radiotherapy</xref>.         </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>
For 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 with cancer, 
                                <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_radiotherapy_diagnosis__icd_">RADIOTHERAPY DIAGNOSIS (ICD)</xref>
 is the primary tumour diagnosis code                    </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>
For non-cancer diagnoses, 
                                <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_radiotherapy_diagnosis__icd_">RADIOTHERAPY DIAGNOSIS (ICD)</xref>
 is the main condition being treated during the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_radiotherapy_episode">Radiotherapy Episode</xref>.                    </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
